snippet.title: Kotha Hoyechhilo | কথা হয়েছিল । Troyee | Bengali Movie Song | Asha Bhosle Song

localized.description:
Bengali film song Kotha Hoyechhilo... from the movie Troyee released in the year 1982 starring Mithun Chakraborty and Debasree Roy. And Sung by Asha Bhosle. 

Song Name : Kotha Hoyechilo
Artist : Asha Bhosle
Lyricist : Swapan Chakraborty
Music Director : Rahul Deb Burman
Movie : Troyee
Release : 1982
Director : Goutam Mukherjee
Star Cast : Mithun Chakraborty,Debashree Roy,Soumitra Banerjee
